  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065870/extras/fee3176643dda4b3312244e3d29960ac.avif?t=1716090755\" width=600 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><strong>• Stone Bag</strong><br>Fill your stone bag with Yin(black) and Yang(white) stones. You need to randomly pick your stone in the right order to cast your skills. Balance the amount of Yin and Yang stones to increase the possibility of perfect casting.<br><strong>• Deck Building</strong><br>Choose your favorite school and skills! You may obtain more passives and skill books during each attempt. Some skills have multiple volumes. Equipping them at the same time will power up the skill massively. <br><strong>• Map Exploration</strong><br>Pick your own path on the map. You need to manage the use of your limited energy bar. It’s up to you to explore every single tile or to skip some battles.<br><br>Most Importantly, here is a cat!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065870/extras/73a9f693d4c0d0bdc6b1f5e7cc763065.poster.avif?t=1716090755\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065870/extras/73a9f693d4c0d0bdc6b1f5e7cc763065.webm?t=1716090755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065870/extras/73a9f693d4c0d0bdc6b1f5e7cc763065.mp4?t=1716090755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065870/extras/fee3176643dda4b3312244e3d29960ac.avif?t=1716090755\" width=600 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><strong>• Stone Bag</strong><br>Fill your stone bag with Yin(black) and Yang(white) stones. You need to randomly pick your stone in the right order to cast your skills. Balance the amount of Yin and Yang stones to increase the possibility of perfect casting.<br><strong>• Deck Building</strong><br>Choose your favorite school and skills! You may obtain more passives and skill books during each attempt. Some skills have multiple volumes. Equipping them at the same time will power up the skill massively. <br><strong>• Map Exploration</strong><br>Pick your own path on the map. You need to manage the use of your limited energy bar. It’s up to you to explore every single tile or to skip some battles.<br><br>Most Importantly, here is a cat!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065870/extras/73a9f693d4c0d0bdc6b1f5e7cc763065.poster.avif?t=1716090755\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065870/extras/73a9f693d4c0d0bdc6b1f5e7cc763065.webm?t=1716090755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065870/extras/73a9f693d4c0d0bdc6b1f5e7cc763065.mp4?t=1716090755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
